1)Go to https://start.spring.io
2)Fill in project details:
-Project: Maven
-Language: Java
-Spring Boot: (choose stable, e.g., 3.3.x)
-Group: com.example
-Artifact: name of the project

3)Dependencies: e.g.
-Spring Boot DevTools Developer Tools
-Spring Web
-Spring Data JPA
-MySQL Driver
-Thymeleaf

4)Click Generate – it will download a .zip.

5)Extract the .zip.

6)In IntelliJ:
Click File → Open
Select the extracted project folder (the one with pom.xml inside).
